ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectMutual Logistic support arrangements for defence forces
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of National Defence to transfer, lease or loan logistic supplies to forces of any state that allied or associated with Canada and is a signatory to a mutual logistic support arrangement with Canada, in order to facilitate combined exercises, training, deployments, operations, or other cooperative efforts.
